headline: Molina Healthcare’s (NYSE:MOH) Q1: Beats On Revenue
summary: Healthcare insurance company Molina Healthcare (NYSE:MOH) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q1 CY2025, with sales up 12.2% year on year to $11.15 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $6.08 per share was 2.1% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
